quran[6{c,v,t}:
3,10,"jin logon ne kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai, inhen Allah ke muqablay mein nah unn ka maal kuch kaam day ga, nah aulaad woh dozakh ka eendhan ban kar rahen ge"
3,11,"unn ka injaam waisa hi hoga, jaissa firaon ke sathiyon aur unn se pehlay ke na farmanoon ka ho chuka hai ke onhon ne ayaat Ellahi ko jhutlaya, nateeja yeh howa ke Allah ne un ke gunaaho par inhen pakar liya aur haq yeh hai ke Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai"
3,12,"pas ae Muammad Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam!jin logon ne tumhari dawat ko qubool karne se inkaar kar diya hai, unn se keh do ke qareeb hai woh waqt, jab tum maghloob ho jao ge aur jahannum ki taraf hankayjao ge aur jahannum bara hi bura thikana hai"
3,13,"tumahray liye unn do garohoon mein aik nishaan Ibrat tha, jo ( badar mein ) aik dosray se nbrd aazma hue aik giroh Allah ki raah mein lar raha tha aur dosra giroh kafir tha dekhnay walay bchshm sir dekh rahay thay ke kafir giroh momin giroh se do chand hai magar ( nateejay ne saabit kar diya ke ) Allah apni fatah o nusrat se jis ko chahta hai, madad deta hai دیدۂ Beena rakhnay walon ke liye is mein bara sabaq posheeda hai"
3,14,"logon ke liye marghobaat-e- nafs, aurtain, olaad , sonay chandi ke dhair, cheeda ghoray, maweshi o ray zarayi zameenen barri khush aaind bana di gayi hain, magar yeh sab duniya ki chand roza zindagi ke samaan hain haqeeqat mein jo behtar thikana hai, woh to Allah ke paas hai"
3,15,"kaho : mein tumhe batau ke un se ziyada achi cheez kya hai? jo log taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar karen, unn ke liye un ke Rab ke pa seen baagh hain, jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi, wahan inhen hameshgi ki zindagi haasil hogi, pakeeza biwiyan un ki Rafeeq hon gi aur Allah ki Raza se woh Sarfraz hon ge Allah apne bundon ke ravayye par gehri nazar rakhta hai"
